text: Michelle Strinden is an American politician who has been the 40th lieutenant governor of North Dakota since 2024. She was a member of the North Dakota House of Representatives from the 41st district from 2018 to 2024. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:People from Grand Forks, North Dakota Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians Category:Lieutenant Governors of North Dakota
